<plot>A "Sex and the City" with fur, BearCity follows the adventures of Tyler, an adorable 21-year-old and his pack of bear and cub friends as they gear up for a big party weekend. Tyler has his eyes on Roger, the hottest - and most narcissistic - musclebear in the tri-state area, while finding himself at the center of a potentially messy love triangle with his roommates Fred and Brent, a monogamous bear couple contemplating, and not seeing eye-to-eye about, an open relationship. Add in a handful of friends with their own problems and romantic complications, and the fur is flying!</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?062036</url></doc>
